## 6. Master Comparison Table

| | Serial | Parallel | CMS | G1 |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Threads | 1 | N (STW only) | 1 young(N)/old(concurrent) | N (mostly concurrent) |
| Old gen algorithm | Mark-Sweep-Compact | Mark-Sweep-Compact | Mark-Sweep (no compact) | Mark-Copy (region-based, compacts) |
| Compaction | Always | Always | **Never** | Yes, incremental |
| Fragmentation risk | None | None | **High** | None |
| Optimizes for | Simplicity | Throughput | Latency | Latency + predictability |
| Concurrency algorithm | N/A | N/A | Incremental update + card table | SATB + remembered sets |
| Pause control | None | None | Threshold-based | Goal-based (`MaxGCPauseMillis`) |
| Default in | — | Java 8 | never default | Java 9+ |
| Status | Available | Available | Removed (Java 14) | Active default |

