## 8. Key JVM Flags Cheat Sheet

```bash
-XX:+UseSerialGC
-XX:+UseParallelGC
-XX:+UseConcMarkSweepGC     # Java 8–13 only
-XX:+UseG1GC
-XX:+UseZGC
-XX:+UseShenandoahGC

-Xms4g -Xmx4g                          # heap sizing
-XX:MaxGCPauseMillis=200               # G1 pause goal
-XX:G1HeapRegionSize=8m                # G1 region size
-XX:CMSInitiatingOccupancyFraction=70  # CMS cycle trigger %
-Xlog:gc*:file=gc.log                  # Java 9+ unified GC logging
```
